## Introduction

This project aims to perform forecasting in R using ARIMA modeling, autocorrelation functions, and ETS models. The Image below displays the ARIMA forecast gotten when running all code.

## Data Preparation

To get this analysis started, the CNAGDP.csv file from the Federal Reserve of Economic Data (FRED) is read in. Some pre-processing steps involve turning it into a time series tibble and visualizing the data.
